title: Meet Kylie Jenner's New $50,000 Dog, Rolly
text:
Kylie Jenner and her boyfriend, Tyga, are now proud parents! Don't worry, Kylie isn't preggers, but she does now proudly parents of a very adorable merle tri English Bulldog, named Rolly. Kylie already has two miniature Greyhounds, so at least the adorable little guy will have friends. ​
According to TMZ , he showed up on their doorstep Thursday night with the help of website that sells very expen$$$ive dogs. And by very expen$$$ive, I mean $50,000. To buy a dog. You know, those adorable creatures you can adopt for cheap at a shelter so they don't die? You can also buy them for $50,000! Who needs a super nice car or a downpayment on a house when you can... not have those things?
Advertisement - Continue Reading Below Apparently Rolly was a gift from the CEO of an app that Kylie and Tyga helped shill. Hooray!
